    },
    "time_stamp": "2019-10-31 08:15:09",
    "text": "so here’s the gory aftermath of this attempt."
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Melinda Green",
      "poster_handle": "melinda.green"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2019-10-31 08:16:50",
    "text": "can’t do AJAX load because it brings the child page’s CSS along with it, which includes bootstrap, which interferes with whatever framework is on the blog post itself. and when you try to namespace bootstrap, very many bad things happen. trust me on this."
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Melinda Green",
      "poster_handle": "melinda.green"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2019-10-31 08:16:51",
    "text": "THEN"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Melinda Green",
      "poster_handle": "melinda.green"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2019-10-31 08:18:51",
    "text": "can’t do iframe because the animations were built to run on viewport visibility.  when you load the child page into the iframe, it’s immediately all “visible” in the context of the frame. and all the animations run instantly. so the child page animates as it’s rendering, not on scroll.\n\ni could do a small, scrolling iframe, but then what’s the point? it’s useless."
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Melinda Green",
      "poster_handle": "melinda.green"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2019-10-31 08:19:14",
    "text": "we’ve had three devs talking this over ad nauseum"
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Melinda Green",
      "poster_handle": "melinda.green"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2019-10-31 08:20:03",
    "text": "and we can’t even put it on a standalone page because we’d need to use the site header and footer, which circles right back to where we started with AJAX and iframe."
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Melinda Green",
      "poster_handle": "melinda.green"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2019-10-31 08:20:11",
    "text": "it seemed so easy. and yet…. not possible."
  },
  {
    "poster": {
      "poster_name": "Chad Pierce",
      "poster_handle": "chadbluleadz"
    },
    "time_stamp": "2019-10-31 09:07:43",
